lead_paragraph: Mr. Duterte, the mayor of Davao City, appeared to have an unbeatable lead in the presidential race.

byline.contributor: Richard C. Paddock reported from Manila, and Floyd Whaley from Davao City, the Philippines.
byline.original: By RICHARD C. PADDOCK and FLOYD WHALEY

headline.main: Rodrigo Duterte’s Rivals Concede in Philippine Election

snippet: Mr. Duterte, the mayor of Davao City, appeared to have an unbeatable lead in the presidential race.
